snippet.title: PM Modi Briefed At Army's War Room Over Terror Camps In Pakistan

localized.description:
At the time when angst against Pakistan is at the peak after the Uri attack, which martyred 18 Indian soldiers, and injured several others; India is chalking out its strategy to give it back to Pakistan in the strongest way possible. Prime Minister Narendra Modi spent 2 hours in the War Room, in the South Block for the same.
